{"tid":383292,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"睇翁靜晶fb先知貓糧狗糧食水咁深","createTime":"2017-09-01T11:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T05:43:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a0b835c3210b383c32babe3fa67ddb892eeec7","tid":383292,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"早前去英國的最大收穫，就是搭通了購買及運送優質貓糧/狗糧來港的途徑。這要多得香港及英國兩邊義工的幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n英國那邊，通過Facebook 認識了Gowers Patricia, 她本身是香港移民，熟悉進出口貿易和各項報關規定。英國方面的收貨及包裝，還有Mabel Yeung, 她也是Facebook 認識的義氣仔女，這一大堆的紙箱，就是靠Mabel負責重新包裝，和驗收貨品的。<br />\n<br />\n香港方，有 Kammi Oo 。她負責收集義工的訂單，再將所需物品的清單提交英國的供應商。<br />\n<br />\n可以告訴大家，與西人交易並不是想像中的容易。他們一星期只上班五天，負責人隨時放假，連續一星期無影無蹤，完全是優哉游哉，皇帝不急太監急。<br />\n<br />\n貨物總算是到齊了，上船就可以付運香港。這是我們的大規模「首航」，如果順利的話，港英團隊就可以定期為有需要的動物義工團體服務了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每10萬元的優質食糧，可以省下20萬，連運費在內，大概是香港零售價的三分之一，差價和利潤確是驚人。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n義工用成本價做代購，出心出力只希望減輕各組織的負擔，就此衷心對港英代購團隊，以及本港所有義工致敬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/weng.jingmaryjeanlau/posts/10213771333985134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fweng.jingmaryjeanlau%2Fposts%2F10213771333985134&d=rMgaN5TqaeNk4%2FQu35GHkNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c6a6470a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/weng.jingmaryjeanlau/posts/10213771333985134</a>"},{"pid":"5ef918ea7134f31234329ad6e38c83c23bd443d0","tid":383292,"uid":31254,"like":11,"dislike":16,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"三分二都叫深？<br />\n唔洗交租請人？"},{"pid":"902606a7780c71dc39c64d736ca363f90affc79a","tid":383292,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"知左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲大代理控制左價格唔比賣平<br />\n你賣得平就唔比貨你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096c8302aebcb87445baece155ab602b08d96cfa","tid":383292,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"做熟客仔加買得多 可以做到比建議售價更平<br />\n<br />\n前題係 大家都唔好比代理知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63dc116e7151d086f73ce6a29f4d77ffff75386","tid":383292,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11cec6067b51b97c5f9a830d36f18333533fc235","tid":383292,"uid":30487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"香港買乜都食水勁深"},{"pid":"0344a243cf54db0fc2045871295e5cecf8816e10","tid":383292,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"581c2f8ad20f9b6bb52af86f73c3d4c6981e7c9f","tid":383292,"uid":31254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三分二都叫深？<br />\n唔洗交租請人？</blockquote><br />\n三倍呀傻閪</blockquote><br />\n三你老母倍咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e444380f3a0e6fed383056b096ebe8abc369ea78","tid":383292,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:19:52.000Z","msg":"我睇唔明紅字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0650a4dd698bd80765e2dd06dd42e3076a0577de","tid":383292,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:41:28.000Z","msg":"唔撚識計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買10萬點慳左20萬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母數學好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：數學2"},{"pid":"d903345fef6bf2ba6dcf586ce31eee8b927fa146","tid":383292,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:44:21.000Z","msg":"網購一定便"},{"pid":"b6bef415c65da02c4b00418c40d9e588f7b550a3","tid":383292,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:46:42.000Z","msg