s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買10萬點慳左20萬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母數學好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：數學2</blockquote><br />\n咁簡單都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1171ee32637b0e789efedf7cbdb88280b2b0d60a","tid":383292,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:52:18.000Z","msg":"你去藥房買野都係啦"},{"pid":"fbc546bb4af5a628cdc4b2224cd68fe0c702f137","tid":383292,"uid":40633,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三分二都叫深？<br />\n唔洗交租請人？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行家出現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n茶記食肆打大2.5到3倍 （即係你食個乾牛河45蚊 材料費少於15蚊）餐飲打大10到20倍 （即係杯凍啡賣18蚊 材料費少於2蚊）都未必做得住<br />\n<br />\n香港做生意 租金人工先係最大敵人"},{"pid":"b2935002fdb2a2c05e90cfd9c925f54e6348f9b5","tid":383292,"uid":60115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:55:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三分二都叫深？<br />\n唔洗交租請人？</blockquote><br />\n英國夠要交租請人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b680999dbde208f7b0bfb73ff3d9ad034b8e5cd","tid":383292,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三分二都叫深？<br />\n唔洗交租請人？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行家出現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n茶記食肆打大2.5到3倍 （即係你食個乾牛河45蚊 材料費少於15蚊）餐飲打大10到20倍 （即係杯凍啡賣18蚊 材料費少於2蚊）都未必做得住<br />\n<br />\n香港做生意 租金人工先係最大敵人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n15蚊洗撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8e9ba956c6362a5757eeed8a78705578ef014c","tid":383292,"uid":17726,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"唔係話幫鋪同代理，但鋪頭d 租，人工，代理存倉，運輸，全部都要錢。你無得話條朱古力成本好平，盒檸檬茶攞貨個價錢只係零售3分1，Trading 生意就係咁，你唔岩咪買其他brand 囉，總有平有貴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daddfd8604b7ac37895b74a5532329053ea8a77","tid":383292,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T01:02:45.000Z","msg":"人地唔洗賺咩<br />\n其實乜好平，如果以成本論"},{"pid":"c81ee5f06b4ec7298c9ccc97cfbd3e15ba617904","tid":383292,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T01:07:49.000Z","msg":"做生意係咁架啦 唔通唔賺你錢咩<br />\n你不如問英國廠比原材料你自製啊笨"},{"pid":"224b27d0ba7055dd8ca22d5864bccb90311624e7","tid":383292,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T01:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三分二都叫深？<br />\n唔洗交租請人？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行家出現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n茶記食肆打大2.5到3倍 （即係你食個乾牛河45蚊 材料費少於15蚊）餐飲打大10到20倍 （即係杯凍啡賣18蚊 材料費少於2蚊）都未必做得住<br />\n<br />\n香港做生意 租金人工先係最大敵人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n15蚊洗撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD牛好貴嫁<br />\n去街市就知"}]}